      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p><p>Slice your <strong>ciabatta[s] </strong>in half</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> sliced ciabatta</strong>, cut-side-down and cook for 3 min or until lightly toasted</p><p>Once toasted, transfer the <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>ciabatta</strong> to a plate and reserve the pan</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1712328035495-x200.jpg",
