            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> (enough to coat the base of the pan) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> breaded hake </strong>and cook for 4-5 min on each side, or until golden and cooked through – this is your <strong>golden hake</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
